textBody:
K cell may refer to:

* k-cell (mathematics)
* Intestinal cells which synthesize gastric inhibitory polypeptide
* Natural killer cell
* Koniocellular cell
* Knudsen cell
* The unit cube of dimension k
* Kcell, a Kazakhstani mobile phone operator
